Name: SFMOMA
Description: A renowned art museum located in San Francisco, CA that possesses a multitude of internationally-known pieces.

Name: Black Sands Beach
Description: A beach in Marin County, CA that is known for its nameworthy black sand.

Name: It's All Good Bakery
Description: A black-owned bakery in Oakland, CA that services the East Bay with flavorful, world-class baked goods and sweets.

Name: Mt. Diablo
Description: A mountain visible all throughout the Bay Area that has a number of trails to hike and spots to camp at, all of which provide fantastic views of the bay.

Name: Mississippi Petriied Forest
Description: An ethereal petrified forest in Flora, MS that exhibits ancient natural history frozen in modern time.
